claim.claim-text:
The communication device of claim 8, where the first and second ZCZ CCP sequences are obtained by:
selecting (804) sequences A and B that form a complementary pair;
selecting (806) a pair of sign sequences pAi and pBifrom a set of pairs of sign sequences dependent upon the information to be transmitted;
combining (808) the sign sequences pAi and pBi with the complementary pair sequences A and B, respectively, to form a zero correlation zone (ZCZ) concatenated complementary pair (CCP) sequence; and
transmitting ZCZ CCP sequence as the training sequence,
where the pairs of sign sequences are configured such that their combination with complementary pair sequences A and B form the first and second ZCZ CCP sequences.
